{
  "stem": "214.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We lived in an apartment, which was consisted of five rooms and a kitchen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That's how it was called.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But we were a large family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And my grandmother, my mother's mother, who was-- my grandfather, I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He died in [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Zygorev. ?] So my grandmother-- my mother was an only child, so she lived with us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And actually, she was a-- well, as I say, I really was very, very fond of her.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I didn't know my father's mother so well, and I also know that sometimes when she was coming to visit, there was always something, you know.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "She thought that, you know, her son wasn't-- that her daughter-in-law was not a perfect daughter-in-law.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I remember my mother sometimes cried after my grandfather-- mother left.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But my mother's mother was-- I mean, she was really-- she wonderful.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "If you wanted to go to visit a friend, or invite somebody, you know, or go and make your lessons, you know, do your homework, and my mother would say, no, you do it first.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I would always run to my grandmother, and then she would always somehow finagle it out for us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "She died in 1935, I remember that very well.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "She died Erev Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But she was very sick.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "She had high blood pressure and heart conditions, and everything else which comes with old age, especially at that time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And so then-- then I finished school in 1939, and then two months later-- there were-- you know, in a funny way, of course, things were going on in Germany.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And-- and the Poles always said-- you probably know a little bit about Polish history.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "There was this Jozef Piłsudski, who was a great Polish hero.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
